00:21:50,119 --> 00:21:55,599
[SPEAKER_04] Neki mistici pričaju o odajama unutar naše duše,

591
00:21:55,599 --> 00:21:57,279
[SPEAKER_04] o dubini naše duše,

592
00:21:57,279 --> 00:21:59,779
[SPEAKER_04] o tome da se Bog treba nastaniti u nas,

593
00:21:59,779 --> 00:22:02,200
[SPEAKER_04] da je to toliko veliko sveto,

594
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,180
[SPEAKER_04] da je to toliko proživa,

595
00:22:03,180 --> 00:22:05,460
[SPEAKER_04] da imaš na kraju toga i možeš imati samo ekstazu.

596
00:22:05,700 --> 00:22:08,500
[SPEAKER_04] I sad zamislite gdje smo mi od ekstaza i od krivenja

597
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:11,160
[SPEAKER_04] i od odnosa s Otcem koji se u nama nastanjuje.

598
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:14,319
[SPEAKER_04] Sve je to trojstvo, razumijevati Otca Sina,

599
00:22:14,319 --> 00:22:17,099
[SPEAKER_04] Duha Svetog, njegove načine, njegove puteve.

600
00:22:17,099 --> 00:22:20,400
[SPEAKER_04] A zato smo stvoreni.

601
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:25,660
[SPEAKER_04] Poniznost je ključ da možete razumijet službu osozdravljanja

602
00:22:25,660 --> 00:22:27,440
[SPEAKER_04] i da možete razumijet karizme,

603
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:29,319
[SPEAKER_04] da možete razumijet volju Božju.

604
00:22:29,319 --> 00:22:30,420
[SPEAKER_04] Poniznost.

605
00:22:30,420 --> 00:22:33,220
[SPEAKER_04] Ako ne znate li imate poniznosti,

606
00:22:33,220 --> 00:22:35,440
[SPEAKER_04] bacite se na koljena u svojoj osobnoj molitvi,

607
00:22:35,539 --> 00:22:37,700
[SPEAKER_04] molite, Otče, daj mi poniznost,

608
00:22:37,700 --> 00:22:39,180
[SPEAKER_04] pokaži mi oholost,

609
00:22:39,180 --> 00:22:42,000
[SPEAKER_04] pokaži mi gdje sam napuhan,

610
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:44,519
[SPEAKER_04] gdje sam u kontroli,

611
00:22:44,519 --> 00:22:45,700
[SPEAKER_04] gdje sam u legalizmu,

612
00:22:45,700 --> 00:22:47,079
[SPEAKER_04] gdje sam u perfekcionizmu,

613
00:22:47,079 --> 00:22:48,259
[SPEAKER_04] gdje sam u neslobodi.

614
00:22:48,259 --> 00:22:50,680
[SPEAKER_04] Želim te vidjeti onakav kakav jesi.

615
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:52,059
[SPEAKER_04] Ili kako psalmist kaže,

616
00:22:52,059 --> 00:22:53,420
[SPEAKER_04] pokaži mi svoje lice.

617
00:22:53,420 --> 00:22:56,440
[SPEAKER_04] Ne želim biti ovako prosječan vjernik,

618
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:57,799
[SPEAKER_04] ovako živiti, ovako jednostavan,

619
00:22:57,799 --> 00:22:58,599
[SPEAKER_04] priproživot.

620
00:22:58,599 --> 00:23:00,480
[SPEAKER_04] Stvoren sam za ogromne stvari,

621
00:23:00,480 --> 00:23:01,619
[SPEAKER_04] a vidi kakav sam.

622
00:23:01,619 --> 00:23:03,480
[SPEAKER_04] Sigurno sam ja doprinio tome.

623
00:23:03,559 --> 00:23:05,180
[SPEAKER_04] nisi ti krivi jer im sve daješ.

624
00:23:05,180 --> 00:23:09,119
[SPEAKER_04] Poniznost je ključ za razumijevanje

625
00:23:09,119 --> 00:23:11,299
[SPEAKER_04] svakeg svakog dara i svake milosti,

626
00:23:11,299 --> 00:23:12,720
[SPEAKER_04] pa i službe o zdravljanjem.

627
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:19,079
[SPEAKER_04] Ovaj dar ozdravljanja možemo razumijeti

628
00:23:19,079 --> 00:23:21,460
[SPEAKER_04] samo u sklopu navještaja o kraljevstvu nebeskom

629
00:23:21,460 --> 00:23:24,759
[SPEAKER_04] kojeg je Isus došao navijestiti.

630
00:23:24,759 --> 00:23:27,980
[SPEAKER_04] On, kad je bio kršten,

631
00:23:27,980 --> 00:23:30,240
[SPEAKER_04] krenulo je njegovo javno djelovanje.

632
00:23:30,240 --> 00:23:32,680
[SPEAKER_04] I od prvih stvari on govori

633
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:34,880
[SPEAKER_04] približilo se kraljevstvu nebesko.

634
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:38,940
[SPEAKER_04] onda objašnjava, cijelo vrijeme objašnjava

635
00:23:38,940 --> 00:23:40,599
[SPEAKER_04] što je kraljevstvo nebesko.

636
00:23:40,599 --> 00:23:42,579
[SPEAKER_04] Onda daje do znanja

637
00:23:42,579 --> 00:23:44,339
[SPEAKER_04] da su dva kraljevstva na zemlji

638
00:23:44,339 --> 00:23:45,559
[SPEAKER_04] koja se sukobljavaju.

639
00:23:45,559 --> 00:23:48,619
[SPEAKER_04] O tome ću nešto malo poslije pričati.

640
00:23:48,619 --> 00:23:52,700
[SPEAKER_04] On govori da je Sotona svezao

641
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:54,539
[SPEAKER_04] onu ženu, da je on došao nju osloboditi.

642
00:23:56,119 --> 00:23:57,660
[SPEAKER_04] I puno drugih primjera.

643
00:23:57,660 --> 00:23:59,960
[SPEAKER_04] Priča o sukobu dva kraljevstva.

644
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:01,279
[SPEAKER_04] O njegovom kraljevstvu,

645
00:24:01,279 --> 00:24:02,240
[SPEAKER_04] Božem kraljevstvu

646
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:03,440
[SPEAKER_04] i kraljevstvu Sotone

647
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:05,480
[SPEAKER_04] koji upravlja,

648
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:07,259
[SPEAKER_04] on je to knez,

649
00:24:07,259 --> 00:24:08,859
[SPEAKER_04] ona ovoga svijeta,

650
00:24:08,859 --> 00:24:10,160
[SPEAKER_04] tako se nešto izrazio,

651
00:24:10,160 --> 00:24:12,400
[SPEAKER_04] mislim, Pavao u svojoj poslanici.

652
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:15,759
[SPEAKER_04] Znači, postoje dva kraljevstva.

653
00:24:15,759 --> 00:24:17,920
[SPEAKER_04] I kako ćemo mi znat surađiva s Bogom

654
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:19,619
[SPEAKER_04] ako ne razumijemo principe,

655
00:24:19,619 --> 00:24:21,640
[SPEAKER_04] zakone naše kralja,

656
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:22,559
[SPEAKER_04] čije je kraljevstvo?

657
00:24:22,559 --> 00:24:25,460
[SPEAKER_04] Moramo to razumijet

658
00:24:25,460 --> 00:24:26,960
[SPEAKER_04] da bi mogli s njim surađivati.

659
00:24:26,960 --> 00:24:33,200
[SPEAKER_04] Kad je on uskrsnuo od mrtvih,

660
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:36,420
[SPEAKER_04] 40 dana se ukazivao učenicima

661
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:37,940
[SPEAKER_04] i znate o čemu im je pričao?

662
00:24:37,940 --> 00:24:40,359
[SPEAKER_04] O kraljevstvu nebesku.

663
00:24:40,359 --> 00:24:42,519
[SPEAKER_04] Ne znam se ti kao o tome razmišljali.

664
00:24:42,519 --> 00:24:44,319
[SPEAKER_04] Većina nije, 100%.

665
00:24:44,319 --> 00:24:47,039
[SPEAKER_04] 40 dana, prije nego što je otišao

666
00:24:47,039 --> 00:24:48,460
[SPEAKER_04] u nebo kocu,

667
00:24:48,460 --> 00:24:49,519
[SPEAKER_04] da se vrati,

668
00:24:49,519 --> 00:24:50,640
[SPEAKER_04] da pošalja duha svetom,

669
00:24:50,640 --> 00:24:52,500
[SPEAKER_04] on im, kaže evanđelist,

670
00:24:52,500 --> 00:24:54,259
[SPEAKER_04] govori o kraljevstvu nebeskom.

671
00:24:54,259 --> 00:24:57,259
[SPEAKER_04] I sad zamislite vi da ste 40 dana

672
00:24:57,259 --> 00:24:59,400
[SPEAKER_04] s Isusom ili koliko god je on dana

673
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:00,759
[SPEAKER_04] od tih 40 bio s njima,

674
00:25:00,759 --> 00:25:02,299
[SPEAKER_04] da ste sjeli u krug,

675
00:25:02,299 --> 00:25:03,880
[SPEAKER_04] on dođe i on ti objašnjava

676
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:05,019
[SPEAKER_04] kako je kraljevstvo nebesko.

677
00:25:05,019 --> 00:25:06,000
[SPEAKER_04] Kako bi to izgledalo?

678
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:07,180
[SPEAKER_04] On govori, slušajte,

679
00:25:07,180 --> 00:25:08,339
[SPEAKER_04] vako, to vam je tako,

680
00:25:08,339 --> 00:25:09,099
[SPEAKER_04] to vam je tako,

681
00:25:09,099 --> 00:25:09,819
[SPEAKER_04] to vam je tako,

682
00:25:09,819 --> 00:25:10,599
[SPEAKER_04] kraljevstvo nebesko,

683
00:25:10,599 --> 00:25:11,400
[SPEAKER_04] vidite ovo,

684
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,119
[SPEAKER_04] kad napravite ovo,

685
00:25:12,119 --> 00:25:12,599
[SPEAKER_04] onda je ovo.

686
00:25:12,599 --> 00:25:14,240
[SPEAKER_04] Morate vako, morate enako.

687
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,799
[SPEAKER_04] koliko je on njima morao to objašnjavati,

688
00:25:16,799 --> 00:25:17,400
[SPEAKER_04] govoriti.

689
00:25:19,440 --> 00:25:20,359
[SPEAKER_04] I opet,

690
00:25:20,359 --> 00:25:23,359
[SPEAKER_04] to znanje nije bilo dovoljno

691
00:25:23,359 --> 00:25:24,720
[SPEAKER_04] da promijeni njihovo srce.

692
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:26,420
[SPEAKER_04] Trebao je doći duh sveti.

693
00:25:26,420 --> 00:25:29,079
[SPEAKER_04] I večeras ga želi na poseban način

694
00:25:29,079 --> 00:25:31,359
[SPEAKER_04] častiti i dat njemu hvalu i slavu,

695
00:25:31,359 --> 00:25:33,740
[SPEAKER_04] jer je on treća božanska osoba

696
00:25:33,740 --> 00:25:34,819
[SPEAKER_04] za vrijeme crkve,

697
00:25:34,819 --> 00:25:38,440
[SPEAKER_04] od pedesetnice do drugog dolaska.

698
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:40,480
[SPEAKER_04] On je tu da nas uvodi u svu istinu,

699
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:42,039
[SPEAKER_04] on je tu da nas oprema,

700
00:25:42,039 --> 00:25:44,400
[SPEAKER_04] on je tu da nam otkriva volju očevu,

701
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:46,900
[SPEAKER_04] on je tu da nam otkriva očevo lice,

702
00:25:46,900 --> 00:25:48,220
[SPEAKER_04] da nam otkriva sina,

703
00:25:48,220 --> 00:25:50,400
[SPEAKER_04] da nam otkriva dijelo spasenja.

704
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:51,599
[SPEAKER_04] On sve čini,

705
00:25:51,599 --> 00:25:52,920
[SPEAKER_04] on oprema,

706
00:25:53,039 --> 00:25:53,720
[SPEAKER_04] sve on radi.

707
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:55,819
[SPEAKER_04] I ako njega ne poznajemo,

708
00:25:55,819 --> 00:25:58,539
[SPEAKER_04] a zamislite da su naši teolozi

709
00:25:58,539 --> 00:26:00,259
[SPEAKER_04] ustvrdili da je

710
00:26:00,259 --> 00:26:02,460
[SPEAKER_04] duh sveti nepoznati Bog.

711
00:26:02,460 --> 00:26:04,079
[SPEAKER_04] I zamislite,

712
00:26:04,079 --> 00:26:06,579
[SPEAKER_04] ja vjerujem da je

713
00:26:06,579 --> 00:26:08,339
[SPEAKER_04] Isusu bilo otkriveno

714
00:26:08,339 --> 00:26:10,680
[SPEAKER_04] u gecemaniju ili nekim dijelima njegovog života,

715
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:12,059
[SPEAKER_04] da će doći vrijeme crkve

716
00:26:12,059 --> 00:26:13,940
[SPEAKER_04] kad ono zbog čega je on dao

717
00:26:13,940 --> 00:26:15,599
[SPEAKER_04] i rekao, bolje da ja odem

718
00:26:15,599 --> 00:26:18,640
[SPEAKER_04] pa da može duh sveti doći.

719
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,539
[SPEAKER_04] Bolje je da ja odem.

720
00:26:19,539 --> 00:26:21,339
[SPEAKER_04] I ja ću sad dat svoj život.

721
00:26:22,460 --> 00:26:23,039
[SPEAKER_04] dobijat će me.

722
00:26:23,039 --> 00:26:25,839
[SPEAKER_04] Jer to je dobro, jer mora to tako biti.

723
00:26:25,839 --> 00:26:27,519
[SPEAKER_04] On će doći, vaš branitelj.

724
00:26:27,519 --> 00:26:30,859
[SPEAKER_04] I on će vam, sve će raditi za vas.

725
00:26:30,859 --> 00:26:31,920
[SPEAKER_04] U vama će moliti,

726
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:33,299
[SPEAKER_04] otkrivat vam duh posljedstva,

727
00:26:33,299 --> 00:26:34,920
[SPEAKER_04] da ste ljubljena djeca Bože,

728
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:36,180
[SPEAKER_04] otkrivat će vam vašu identitet.

729
00:26:36,740 --> 00:26:39,500
[SPEAKER_04] I onda mu otac siguro otkrio doće vrijeme u crkvi

730
00:26:39,500 --> 00:26:41,319
[SPEAKER_04] kad će to biti nepoznati Bog.

731
00:26:41,319 --> 00:26:45,559
[SPEAKER_04] I neće ljudi znati, kršćani, veliki vjernici,

732
00:26:45,559 --> 00:26:47,740
[SPEAKER_04] neće znat ništa o duhu svetu.

733
00:26:49,380 --> 00:26:51,980
[SPEAKER_04] Mene to iznutra izjede,

734
00:26:51,980 --> 00:26:52,799
[SPEAKER_04] mene uništi,

735
00:26:52,799 --> 00:26:54,099
[SPEAKER_04] mene u meni pobodi

736
00:26:54,099 --> 00:26:55,619
[SPEAKER_04] takvu želju

737
00:26:55,619 --> 00:26:57,579
[SPEAKER_04] da nešto poduzmem

738
00:26:57,579 --> 00:26:59,039
[SPEAKER_04] i promijenim po tom pitanju.

739
00:26:59,039 --> 00:27:00,380
[SPEAKER_04] A znate što?

740
00:27:00,380 --> 00:27:01,500
[SPEAKER_04] Jer smo sebe ljubljni,

741
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:03,059
[SPEAKER_04] okrenuti svojim životima,

742
00:27:03,059 --> 00:27:04,339
[SPEAKER_04] nas nije briga uglavnom.

743
00:27:04,339 --> 00:27:06,680
[SPEAKER_04] Ja znam kako izgleda čovjek

744
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:07,519
[SPEAKER_04] kojeg je nešto briga.

745
00:27:07,980 --> 00:27:09,539
[SPEAKER_04] Katolike nije briga.

746
00:27:09,539 --> 00:27:11,700
[SPEAKER_04] To je tako.

747
00:27:11,700 --> 00:27:13,180
[SPEAKER_04] Većinu katolika.

748
00:27:13,180 --> 00:27:15,400
[SPEAKER_04] Većinu vas nije briga.

749
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:16,920
[SPEAKER_04] Ne uvijek,

750
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,220
[SPEAKER_04] ali većinu vremena.

751
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:19,000
[SPEAKER_04] Nije vas briga.

752
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:20,759
[SPEAKER_04] Jer da vas je briga,

753
00:27:20,759 --> 00:27:22,480
[SPEAKER_04] tražili bi duha svetu

754
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:23,740
[SPEAKER_04] i pitali bi ga

755
00:27:23,740 --> 00:27:24,720
[SPEAKER_04] što želiš da učini.

756
00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:27,359
[SPEAKER_04] Evo službenice gospodine,

757
00:27:27,359 --> 00:27:28,880
[SPEAKER_04] evo službenika gospodine,

758
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,160
[SPEAKER_04] reci mi šta da radi

759
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:31,819
[SPEAKER_04] i svijet bi bio drugačiji.

760
00:27:31,819 --> 00:27:33,940
[SPEAKER_04] Bilo bi više svetih ljudi.

761
00:27:33,940 --> 00:27:35,660
[SPEAKER_04] Bilo bi više čudesa.

762
00:27:35,660 --> 00:27:37,960
[SPEAKER_04] Bilo bi više božje ljubavi u crkvi.

763
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:39,980
[SPEAKER_04] Bilo bi više ozdravljenja

764
00:27:39,980 --> 00:27:41,660
[SPEAKER_04] i scjeljena obiteljskih odnosa.

765
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:43,460
[SPEAKER_04] Bilo bi više božje slave

766
00:27:43,460 --> 00:27:45,160
[SPEAKER_04] i božje svetosti u crkvi.

767
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:46,740
[SPEAKER_04] Jer ona se ne nalazi

768
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:48,339
[SPEAKER_04] u ovoj građavini ovde.

769
00:27:48,339 --> 00:27:50,380
[SPEAKER_04] Tu je presveto,

770
00:27:50,380 --> 00:27:52,240
[SPEAKER_04] ali Bog želi živjeti u svima vama

771
00:27:52,240 --> 00:27:53,960
[SPEAKER_04] i u vama oblikova drugog Krista

772
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:55,140
[SPEAKER_04] da budete poput njega.

773
00:27:55,140 --> 00:27:57,900
[SPEAKER_04] Ne poznajmo duha svetu.

774
00:27:57,900 --> 00:28:00,420
[SPEAKER_04] I kako ćemo mi služiti duhu svetom

775
00:28:00,420 --> 00:28:01,720
[SPEAKER_04] ako ga ne poznajemo?

776
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:04,799
[SPEAKER_04] Kako ćemo mi biti dio kraljestva Božijeg

777
00:28:04,799 --> 00:28:06,279
[SPEAKER_04] ako ne znamo duhovne zakone?

778
00:28:07,180 --> 00:28:08,599
[SPEAKER_04] Mislimo da je dosta doći nedjelju

779
00:28:08,599 --> 00:28:09,380
[SPEAKER_04] na svetu misu,

780
00:28:09,380 --> 00:28:10,859
[SPEAKER_04] ispovjediti se tu i tamo,

781
00:28:10,859 --> 00:28:12,960
[SPEAKER_04] servisirati se i to je to.

782
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:13,920
[SPEAKER_04] To je naše hršćanstvo.

783
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:14,839
[SPEAKER_04] Molimo prije jela,

784
00:28:14,839 --> 00:28:15,740
[SPEAKER_04] prije spavanja,

785
00:28:15,740 --> 00:28:17,920
[SPEAKER_04] a Bog ima cijelo obilje

786
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:19,160
[SPEAKER_04] duhovnog života za vas.

787
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:21,660
[SPEAKER_04] Bog odvan želi jednu takvu intimu

788
00:28:21,660 --> 00:28:23,660
[SPEAKER_04] da vam otkriva po proročkoj službi

789
00:28:23,660 --> 00:28:24,359
[SPEAKER_04] pokrštenja,

790
00:28:24,359 --> 00:28:25,680
[SPEAKER_04] da čujete njegov glas.

791
00:28:26,519 --> 00:28:27,599
[SPEAKER_04] Ali morate znati šta je,

792
00:28:27,599 --> 00:28:28,359
[SPEAKER_04] kakav je Bog,

793
00:28:28,359 --> 00:28:30,019
[SPEAKER_04] da bi znali prepoznat njegov glas.

794
00:28:30,019 --> 00:28:32,440
[SPEAKER_04] Moraš znati njegovu narav i njegov um,

795
00:28:32,440 --> 00:28:33,240
[SPEAKER_04] njegovu riješ,

796
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:35,799
[SPEAKER_04] da bi vidio razlučuje li ovo od Boga ili nije.

797
00:28:35,799 --> 00:28:37,079
[SPEAKER_04] A onda ga ne znaš,

798
00:28:37,079 --> 00:28:38,619
[SPEAKER_04] pa onda šta možeš lupeta gluposti,

799
00:28:38,619 --> 00:28:39,759
[SPEAKER_04] ući nove devijacije,

800
00:28:39,759 --> 00:28:41,940
[SPEAKER_04] crkva će se opet iznova sablažnjavati,

801
00:28:41,940 --> 00:28:43,819
[SPEAKER_04] vidiš ovaj priča da ima dar proroštva,

802
00:28:43,819 --> 00:28:45,519
[SPEAKER_04] priča glupost koja nisu u skladu

803
00:28:45,519 --> 00:28:46,359
[SPEAKER_04] s riječju Božijom,

804
00:28:46,359 --> 00:28:47,460
[SPEAKER_04] sa Božijom voljom

805
00:28:47,460 --> 00:28:48,400
[SPEAKER_04] i s naukom crkve.

806
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:51,259
[SPEAKER_04] I onda od svjedoka postaneš antisvjedok.

807
00:28:51,259 --> 00:28:52,720
[SPEAKER_04] Od onoga ko bi treba uzeti karizme

808
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:53,460
[SPEAKER_04] da izgrađuje crku,

809
00:28:53,460 --> 00:28:54,980
[SPEAKER_04] postaješ onaj koji radi problem

810
00:28:54,980 --> 00:28:55,900
[SPEAKER_04] i razdor u crkvi.

811
00:28:55,900 --> 00:28:57,680
[SPEAKER_04] To nije Božija volja za vaš život.

812
00:28:57,680 --> 00:29:00,259
[SPEAKER_04] Moramo upoznat duha svetu.

813
00:29:00,259 --> 00:29:03,740
[SPEAKER_04] Moramo upoznat principe Božije kraljevstva.

814
00:29:03,740 --> 00:29:06,220
[SPEAKER_04] Poniznost je jedna od najbitnijih stvari.

815
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:08,319
[SPEAKER_04] Ponizite se pred gospodinom

816
00:29:08,319 --> 00:29:09,799
[SPEAKER_04] da vas on može uzdići.

817
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,599
[SPEAKER_04] Ponizite se pred gospodinom

818
00:29:11,599 --> 00:29:13,200
[SPEAKER_04] da može progovoriti vašem srcu.

819
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:19,059
[SPEAKER_04] Molimo toliko često puta oče naš

820
00:29:19,059 --> 00:29:20,940
[SPEAKER_04] i govorimo dođi kraljevstvo tvoje.

821
00:29:20,940 --> 00:29:23,319
[SPEAKER_04] Znate di je njegovo kraljevstvo?

822
00:29:23,319 --> 00:29:25,200
[SPEAKER_04] Spustilo se od ozgo dole

823
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:27,160
[SPEAKER_04] i sad je među nama.

824
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:30,819
[SPEAKER_04] U njegovom kraljevstvu nema smrti.

825
00:29:30,819 --> 00:29:32,960
[SPEAKER_04] U njegovom kraljevstvu nema bolesti.

826
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:35,299
[SPEAKER_04] U njegovom kraljevstvu nema suza.

827
00:29:35,299 --> 00:29:40,160
[SPEAKER_04] U njegovom kraljevstvu je nadnaravan život.

828
00:29:40,200 --> 00:29:45,200
[SPEAKER_04] Njegova kultura kraljevstva Božjeg je nadnaravna.

829
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:49,140
[SPEAKER_04] Jezik kraljevstva Božjeg je nadnaravan.

830
00:29:50,059 --> 00:29:52,000
[SPEAKER_04] jer mi izgledamo nadnaravno

831
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:54,700
[SPEAKER_04] kao ambasadori kraljevstva Božje.

832
00:29:54,700 --> 00:29:55,859
[SPEAKER_04] Izgledamo.

833
00:29:55,859 --> 00:29:57,599
[SPEAKER_04] A čina nas ne izgleda.

834
00:29:57,599 --> 00:29:59,440
[SPEAKER_04] Naš jezik nije nadnaravan.

835
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:01,519
[SPEAKER_04] Naš jezik je često svjetovan.

836
00:30:01,519 --> 00:30:05,559
[SPEAKER_04] Borimo se uglavnom sa osnovnim grijesima,

837
00:30:05,559 --> 00:30:07,319
[SPEAKER_04] temeljne, nikako da se iskobeljamo.

838
00:30:07,319 --> 00:30:10,259
[SPEAKER_04] Ne znamo izađi, ne znamo osvojiti područja

839
00:30:10,259 --> 00:30:13,140
[SPEAKER_04] našeg života, da uđemo u blagoslo.

840
00:30:13,140 --> 00:30:18,799
[SPEAKER_04] Danas mi je Petar rekao jedan vrhonski primjer

841
00:30:18,799 --> 00:30:22,259
[SPEAKER_04] u vezi ovoga da smo mi ambasadori

842
00:30:22,259 --> 00:30:24,519
[SPEAKER_04] kraljevstva Božjeg na zemlji.

843
00:30:24,519 --> 00:30:27,380
[SPEAKER_04] Znamite kad dođe američka ambasada u Hrvatsku.

844
00:30:27,380 --> 00:30:29,700
[SPEAKER_04] Kaže da svaka američka ambasada

845
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:32,160
[SPEAKER_04] u kojoj god zemlji da otvori svoju ambasadu

846
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:33,519
[SPEAKER_04] uvijek ima isti ulaz.

847
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:35,980
[SPEAKER_04] Unutra je sve američko.

848
00:30:35,980 --> 00:30:38,380
[SPEAKER_04] Američki jezik, američka kultura,

849
00:30:38,380 --> 00:30:40,500
[SPEAKER_04] američki vjerojatno namještaj, sve američko.

850
00:30:40,500 --> 00:30:43,039
[SPEAKER_04] Tako bi trebalo biti kraljevstvo Božje

851
00:30:43,039 --> 00:30:44,200
[SPEAKER_04] prisutno u svijetu.

852
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:46,960
[SPEAKER_04] Trebalo bi biti kraljevstvo nebesko.

853
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:50,099
[SPEAKER_04] I onda mi koji radimo, koji smo ambasadori,

854
00:30:50,099 --> 00:30:51,720
[SPEAKER_04] trebali bi biti dio te kulture.

855
00:30:51,720 --> 00:30:54,160
[SPEAKER_04] Kao što su ljudi koji rade u američkoj ambasadi

856
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:55,359
[SPEAKER_04] dio te priče.

857
00:30:55,359 --> 00:31:01,579
[SPEAKER_04] Ono što ja mislim je da crkva može biti obnovljena,

858
00:31:01,579 --> 00:31:03,200
[SPEAKER_04] a duh sveti je želi obnoviti

859
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:06,079
[SPEAKER_04] i zato je podigao katoličku karizmatsku obnovu,

860
00:31:06,079 --> 00:31:08,700
[SPEAKER_04] da je obnovi, da cijela postane obnovljena.

861
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:10,940
[SPEAKER_04] Možemo je obnoviti samo kad shvatimo

862
00:31:10,940 --> 00:31:12,400
[SPEAKER_04] ozbiljno dar duha svetog.

863
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:15,019
[SPEAKER_04] Koliko vas je doživjelo krizmu

864
00:31:15,019 --> 00:31:16,579
[SPEAKER_04] ozbiljno predano

865
00:31:16,579 --> 00:31:20,259
[SPEAKER_04] sa velikim, ono, baš s velikom vjerom

866
00:31:20,259 --> 00:31:22,420
[SPEAKER_04] i s velikim plodovima onda poslije svoje krizme.

867
00:31:22,420 --> 00:31:25,079
[SPEAKER_04] Znamo problem, ja sam slušao predmete

868
00:31:25,079 --> 00:31:31,000
[SPEAKER_04] iz katehizacije puste i na faksu i u crkvi.

869
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:33,319
[SPEAKER_04] Svi govore u ikisti je problem.

870
00:31:33,319 --> 00:31:37,319
[SPEAKER_04] Mladi dođu, odrade krizmu i nestanu.

871
00:31:37,319 --> 00:31:40,680
[SPEAKER_04] Skroz naopako.

872
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:44,160
[SPEAKER_04] Trebalo bi suprotno sakrament kršćanske zrelosti,

873
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:47,480
[SPEAKER_04] gdje bi mi trebali obje opremljeni za dijelo služenja,

874
00:31:47,480 --> 00:31:48,619
[SPEAKER_04] mi odemo.

875
00:31:48,619 --> 00:31:51,380
[SPEAKER_04] A ko nas priprema, kako nas priprema,

876
00:31:51,380 --> 00:31:52,779
[SPEAKER_04] što smo mi tu pristali,

877
00:31:52,779 --> 00:31:55,000
[SPEAKER_04] kakvi smo mi ljudi, šta se s nama događa,

878
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:55,779
[SPEAKER_04] koga briga.

879
00:31:55,779 --> 00:31:57,839
[SPEAKER_04] I mislimo da je sve sve jedno,

880
00:31:57,839 --> 00:32:00,220
[SPEAKER_04] da je Bog, da je to Božje stvari,

881
00:32:00,220 --> 00:32:02,140
[SPEAKER_04] da mi možemo njih koristka,

882
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:02,940
[SPEAKER_04] ako god mi očemo.

883
00:32:02,940 --> 00:32:05,740
[SPEAKER_04] Jedna slika koja mi je bila

884
00:32:05,740 --> 00:32:08,099
[SPEAKER_04] u pripremi ovoga je da mi,

885
00:32:08,099 --> 00:32:10,140
[SPEAKER_04] katolici, svačamo Božje stvari

886
00:32:10,140 --> 00:32:11,420
[SPEAKER_04] kao švedski stol.

887
00:32:12,460 --> 00:32:14,599
[SPEAKER_04] Ovo ću uzeti, ovo neću uzeti.

888
00:32:14,599 --> 00:32:16,319
[SPEAKER_04] Ovo mi odgovara, viš, ovo ne.

889
00:32:16,319 --> 00:32:18,019
[SPEAKER_04] Nije me briga što da misliš,

890
00:32:18,019 --> 00:32:18,759
[SPEAKER_04] daj mi ovo.

891
00:32:18,759 --> 00:32:21,440
[SPEAKER_04] I znate što mi radimo, da ni ne znamo.

892
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:23,420
[SPEAKER_04] Ulazimo u veliku kontrolu,

893
00:32:23,420 --> 00:32:28,319
[SPEAKER_04] a sve to pismo u Starom Zavetu kaže

894
00:32:28,319 --> 00:32:32,519
[SPEAKER_04] da duh kontrole donosi duh vraćanja sa sobom.

895
00:32:32,519 --> 00:32:36,259
[SPEAKER_04] Mi ni ne znamo da želimo instrumentalizira

896
00:32:36,259 --> 00:32:37,740
[SPEAKER_04] Božju milo za naše dobro,

897
00:32:37,740 --> 00:32:39,740
[SPEAKER_04] ponome kako mi mislimo da treba biti.

898
00:32:40,799 --> 00:32:42,920
[SPEAKER_04] Pa onda se oženim, pa za mjesec dana

899
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,099
[SPEAKER_04] tražim razvod braka.

900
00:32:44,099 --> 00:32:47,099
[SPEAKER_04] Pošaljam djecu samo da odrade

901
00:32:47,099 --> 00:32:48,759
[SPEAKER_04] ove sakramente.

902
00:32:48,759 --> 00:32:51,119
[SPEAKER_04] Molim kad mi je teško.

903
00:32:51,119 --> 00:32:53,660
[SPEAKER_04] Čitam riječ, eto zato,

904
00:32:53,660 --> 00:32:55,240
[SPEAKER_04] da mi bude ljepše u životu.

905
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:57,940
[SPEAKER_04] To je švedski stol.

906
00:32:57,940 --> 00:32:59,599
[SPEAKER_04] To je duhovno švedskog stola.

907
00:32:59,599 --> 00:33:02,759
[SPEAKER_04] To nije odnos prema dobrom Bogu Otcu,

908
00:33:02,759 --> 00:33:05,319
[SPEAKER_04] koji je milosredan velik,

909
00:33:05,319 --> 00:33:06,240
[SPEAKER_04] naprava sve za nas,

910
00:33:06,240 --> 00:33:07,279
[SPEAKER_04] koji nas zove u suradnju

911
00:33:07,279 --> 00:33:09,420
[SPEAKER_04] i želi nam dati svoj plan

912
00:33:09,420 --> 00:33:10,759
[SPEAKER_04] i svrhu za naš život.

913
00:33:10,799 --> 00:33:12,920
[SPEAKER_04] ponašamo se grozno

914
00:33:12,920 --> 00:33:15,039
[SPEAKER_04] i mislimo da je to okej.

915
00:33:15,039 --> 00:33:16,420
[SPEAKER_04] Ali to nije okej.

916
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:17,160
[SPEAKER_04] Evo, ja ću vam reći,

917
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,099
[SPEAKER_04] to nije okej.

918
00:33:24,599 --> 00:33:27,920
[SPEAKER_04] U mnogim djelovima crkve snaga duha svetog

919
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:29,839
[SPEAKER_04] i njegovih karizmi je marginalizirana.

920
00:33:29,839 --> 00:33:31,660
[SPEAKER_04] U najgorem slučaju,

921
00:33:31,660 --> 00:33:34,759
[SPEAKER_04] doživljavaju se kao neobvezatne,

922
00:33:34,759 --> 00:33:37,980
[SPEAKER_04] ta duhovno se doživlja kao neobvezatna

923
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:38,599
[SPEAKER_04] i čudna,

924
00:33:38,599 --> 00:33:41,099
[SPEAKER_04] ili je se osuđuje kao neprijatelja

925
00:33:41,099 --> 00:33:42,539
[SPEAKER_04] sakramentalne milosti

926
00:33:42,539 --> 00:33:44,119
[SPEAKER_04] i osobne svetosti.

927
00:33:46,279 --> 00:33:48,660
[SPEAKER_04] Ja znam koliko komentara

928
00:33:48,660 --> 00:33:50,000
[SPEAKER_04] o karizmaticima kruži.

929
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,599
[SPEAKER_04] Znate koje su to grozne stvari.

930
00:33:51,599 --> 00:33:53,019
[SPEAKER_04] Ljudi se Boga ne boje.

931
00:33:53,019 --> 00:33:54,519
[SPEAKER_04] Ne razumiju,

932
00:33:54,519 --> 00:33:55,660
[SPEAKER_04] a imaju mišljenje.

933
00:33:55,660 --> 00:33:57,980
[SPEAKER_04] To je valjda prosječan Hrvat katolik.

934
00:33:57,980 --> 00:33:58,940
[SPEAKER_04] Ne razumijem,

935
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:00,460
[SPEAKER_04] nisam čak nišao vidjet,

936
00:34:00,460 --> 00:34:01,680
[SPEAKER_04] ali imam mišljenje.

937
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:04,000
[SPEAKER_04] Ja sam čuo za jednog svećanika

938
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:05,200
[SPEAKER_04] koji je pisao knjigu

939
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,759
[SPEAKER_04] o karizmatskoj obnovi

940
00:34:06,759 --> 00:34:09,579
[SPEAKER_04] i ovoj našoj duhovnosti.

941
00:34:09,579 --> 00:34:11,280
[SPEAKER_04] Nikad nije bio na nekoj zajednici

942
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,780
[SPEAKER_04] ili nekoj molitvi

943
00:34:12,780 --> 00:34:13,659
[SPEAKER_04] ili nekom susretu.

944
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:15,679
[SPEAKER_04] Ali on piše knjigu legenda.

945
00:34:15,679 --> 00:34:19,280
[SPEAKER_04] Kako je to uvrnuto?

946
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:24,659
[SPEAKER_04] Mi nismo samo izbornici za nogometa.

947
00:34:24,659 --> 00:34:25,519
[SPEAKER_04] Znate kako kažu

948
00:34:25,519 --> 00:34:27,159
[SPEAKER_04] kao igra Hrvatska nogometna reprezentacija.

949
00:34:27,159 --> 00:34:28,380
[SPEAKER_04] Četiri milijuna izbornika.

950
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:29,780
[SPEAKER_04] Sad nas je manje.

951
00:34:29,780 --> 00:34:31,440
[SPEAKER_04] Tri milijuna i osasto.

952
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:33,500
[SPEAKER_04] E tako vam je s Božim stvarima.

953
00:34:33,500 --> 00:34:35,420
[SPEAKER_04] Kad neko nešto radi

954
00:34:35,420 --> 00:34:36,960
[SPEAKER_04] u crkvi malo podigne prašinu

955
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:39,940
[SPEAKER_04] imamo bar pola milijuna izbornika

956
00:34:39,940 --> 00:34:41,159
[SPEAKER_04] koji imaju o tome mišljenje.

957
00:34:41,159 --> 00:34:43,000
[SPEAKER_04] Bez odgovornosti,

958
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:43,820
[SPEAKER_04] bez dubine,

959
00:34:44,099 --> 00:34:44,900
[SPEAKER_04] bez poštenja,

960
00:34:44,900 --> 00:34:48,460
[SPEAKER_04] bez ono želje da nađu istinu.

961
00:34:48,460 --> 00:34:50,039
[SPEAKER_04] I to ne funkcionira tako.

962
00:34:50,039 --> 00:34:53,760
[SPEAKER_04] Ono što je dobro,

963
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:56,119
[SPEAKER_04] malo sam vas sad ispleskom,

964
00:34:56,119 --> 00:34:58,500
[SPEAKER_04] ali tako ja funkcioniram.

965
00:34:58,500 --> 00:34:59,699
[SPEAKER_04] To je škabrinski dio mene.

966
00:35:02,340 --> 00:35:03,960
[SPEAKER_04] želim vam reći radusnu vijest.

967
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:06,880
[SPEAKER_04] Bog vam želi dati nove izljave duha svijetom.

968
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:08,480
[SPEAKER_04] On ima puno,

969
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,940
[SPEAKER_04] on ima u izobilju

970
00:35:09,940 --> 00:35:11,860
[SPEAKER_04] i on jedva čeka dati još.

971
00:35:12,820 --> 00:35:14,440
[SPEAKER_04] pitanje je želite li vi još.

972
00:35:14,440 --> 00:35:17,440
[SPEAKER_04] U dijelima dva oni doželjaju pedesetnicu.

973
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:22,739
[SPEAKER_04] jedna od najljepših stvari meni u cijeloj Bibliji su dijela četiri.

974
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:23,800
[SPEAKER_04] Ne znam,

975
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:25,599
[SPEAKER_04] malo su mi trenutno dražao dijela dva.

976
00:35:25,599 --> 00:35:26,980
[SPEAKER_04] Dijela četiri,

977
00:35:26,980 --> 00:35:29,239
[SPEAKER_04] događa se nova pedesetnica,

978
00:35:29,239 --> 00:35:31,380
[SPEAKER_04] zove mala pedesetnica,

979
00:35:31,380 --> 00:35:35,480
[SPEAKER_04] Petar i Ivan su ozdravili onog uzetog,

980
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:37,980
[SPEAKER_04] crkvene vlasti,

981
00:35:37,980 --> 00:35:41,420
[SPEAKER_04] religijski vođe su ih uhvatili,

982
00:35:41,420 --> 00:35:42,340
[SPEAKER_04] u dijelima tri,

983
00:35:42,340 --> 00:35:43,940
[SPEAKER_04] opomenuli ih,

