1152
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:56,699
[SPEAKER_04] neka sekundarna stvar.

1153
00:39:56,699 --> 00:39:58,219
[SPEAKER_04] Oni su sastavni dio

1154
00:39:58,219 --> 00:39:59,679
[SPEAKER_04] prve crkve.

1155
00:40:01,019 --> 00:40:03,340
[SPEAKER_04] moja osobno želja

1156
