1179
00:40:46,019 --> 00:40:48,219
[SPEAKER_04] Koliko tabernakula

1180
00:40:48,219 --> 00:40:49,300
[SPEAKER_04] postoji diljem svijeta.

1181
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,679
