[SPEAKER_04] pravednosti živimo.

1407
00:46:59,079 --> 00:47:01,159
[SPEAKER_04] On čijom se modricom izliječiste.

1408
00:47:01,159 --> 00:47:04,639
[SPEAKER_04] Mi vidimo

1409
