[SPEAKER_04] da je Bog na strani zdravlja.

1410
00:47:06,699 --> 00:47:08,039
[SPEAKER_04] Vi još u starom zavijetu

1411
00:47:08,039 --> 00:47:09,739
[SPEAKER_04] imamo

1412
00:47:09,739 --> 00:47:12,920
[SPEAKER_04] da boraja sam

1413
00:47:12,920 --> 00:47:13,719
[SPEAKER_04] koji je to

1414
00:47:13,719 --> 00:47:14,480
[SPEAKER_04] citat.

1415
00:47:14,480 --> 00:47:16,980
[SPEAKER_04] Naću ga posliju pa ću ga reći.

1416
00:47:16,980 --> 00:47:17,940
[SPEAKER_04] Bog je rekao

1417
00:47:17,940 --> 00:47:18,400
[SPEAKER_04] ja sam Bog

1418
00:47:18,400 --> 00:47:19,260
[SPEAKER_04] koji daje zdravlje.

1419
00:47:19,260 --> 00:47:20,960
[SPEAKER_04] On je očitova

1420
00:47:20,960 --> 00:47:21,739
[SPEAKER_04] jedan dio sebe.

1421
00:47:22,619 --> 00:47:24,000
[SPEAKER_04] Znate što je identitet?

