1425
00:47:26,559 --> 00:47:28,460
[SPEAKER_04] Jedan dio Božjeg identiteta

1426
00:47:28,460 --> 00:47:29,019
[SPEAKER_04] je da on Bog

1427
00:47:29,019 --> 00:47:29,900
[SPEAKER_04] koji daje zdravlje.

1428
00:47:29,900 --> 00:47:31,940
[SPEAKER_04] On daje zdravlje.

1429
00:47:31,940 --> 00:47:33,119
[SPEAKER_04] On je na strani zdravlje.

1430
00:47:33,119 --> 00:47:33,880
[SPEAKER_04] On daje život.

1431
00:47:33,880 --> 00:47:35,199
[SPEAKER_04] U nebu nema bolestnih.

1432
00:47:35,199 --> 00:47:36,599
[SPEAKER_04] Kogod je bil s Bogom

1433
00:47:36,599 --> 00:47:37,440
[SPEAKER_04] nije bolestan.

1434
00:47:37,440 --> 00:47:38,880
[SPEAKER_04] U nebu ćete biti

1435
