[SPEAKER_04] u top formi.

1436
00:47:39,679 --> 00:47:41,880
[SPEAKER_04] Bićete najbolja verzija sebe.

1437
00:47:41,880 --> 00:47:43,519
[SPEAKER_04] Imaćete uskrsnulo tijelo

1438
00:47:43,519 --> 00:47:44,440
[SPEAKER_04] sa pločicama.

1439
00:47:44,440 --> 00:47:46,079
[SPEAKER_04] Bićete mladi

1440
00:47:46,079 --> 00:47:47,219
[SPEAKER_04] u ono

1441
00:47:47,219 --> 00:47:48,380
[SPEAKER_04] najljepši razvoj

1442
00:47:48,380 --> 00:47:49,500
[SPEAKER_04] koji možete zavijeti za sebe.

1443
00:47:49,579 --> 00:47:50,380
[SPEAKER_04] takvi ćete biti.

1444
00:47:50,380 --> 00:47:51,940
[SPEAKER_04] Gori nema invalida,

1445
00:47:51,940 --> 00:47:53,019
[SPEAKER_04] nema ljudi bez oka,

1446
00:47:53,019 --> 00:47:54,079
[SPEAKER_04] nema ljudi

1447
00:47:54,079 --> 00:47:55,579
[SPEAKER_04] sa lošom kosom,

1448
00:47:55,579 --> 00:47:57,199
[SPEAKER_04] sa lošom frizurom,

1449
00:47:57,199 --> 00:47:58,519
[SPEAKER_04] nema sala gore.

1450
00:47:58,519 --> 00:48:00,519
[SPEAKER_04] Nema ga.

1451
00:48:00,519 --> 00:48:02,360
[SPEAKER_04] Bog je mlad,

1452
00:48:02,360 --> 00:48:03,320
[SPEAKER_04] Bog je životan,

1453
00:48:03,320 --> 00:48:04,820
[SPEAKER_04] Bog je snažan.

1454
00:48:04,820 --> 00:48:06,780
[SPEAKER_04] I on otkriva,

1455
00:48:06,780 --> 00:48:08,739
