[SPEAKER_04] dolazi na zemlju,

1459
00:48:12,400 --> 00:48:13,119
[SPEAKER_04] on to donosi.

1460
00:48:13,119 --> 00:48:14,539
[SPEAKER_04] On donosi život i zdravlje.

1461
00:48:14,539 --> 00:48:16,059
[SPEAKER_04] I zato Bog ozdravlja.

1462
00:48:16,059 --> 00:48:17,539
[SPEAKER_04] I zato mi moramo

1463
