1477
00:48:34,000 --> 00:48:36,099
[SPEAKER_04] I to je tako.

1478
00:48:38,860 --> 00:48:41,000
[SPEAKER_04] U Matej 10.7.8 kaže

1479
00:48:41,000 --> 00:48:42,199
[SPEAKER_04] putem propovjedate

1480
00:48:42,199 --> 00:48:42,920
[SPEAKER_04] približilo se

1481
00:48:42,920 --> 00:48:43,860
[SPEAKER_04] kraljevstvo nebesko.

1482
00:48:43,860 --> 00:48:44,760
[SPEAKER_04] Bolesne liječite,

1483
00:48:44,760 --> 00:48:46,239
[SPEAKER_04] mrtve uskrisujte,

1484
00:48:46,239 --> 00:48:47,099
[SPEAKER_04] gubave čistite,

1485
00:48:47,099 --> 00:48:48,099
[SPEAKER_04] zloduhe izgonite.

1486
00:48:48,099 --> 00:48:49,400
[SPEAKER_04] Besplatno primiste,

1487
00:48:49,400 --> 00:48:50,320
[SPEAKER_04] besplatno dajte.

1488
00:48:50,320 --> 00:48:53,179
[SPEAKER_04] Što su besplatno primili?

1489
00:48:53,179 --> 00:48:54,320
[SPEAKER_04] Nadnaravnu službu.

1490
00:48:54,320 --> 00:48:56,519
[SPEAKER_04] Nisu primili neko znanje.

1491
00:48:56,519 --> 00:48:57,980
[SPEAKER_04] Pa da moraju

1492
00:48:57,980 --> 00:48:58,880
[SPEAKER_04] poučavati ljude

1493
00:48:58,880 --> 00:48:59,400
[SPEAKER_04] besplatno.

1494
00:48:59,400 --> 00:48:59,639
[SPEAKER_04] Ajde,

1495
00:48:59,639 --> 00:49:00,800
[SPEAKER_04] na održini neki tamo

1496
00:49:00,800 --> 00:49:01,500
[SPEAKER_04] pet nagovora

1497
00:49:01,500 --> 00:49:02,579
[SPEAKER_04] besplatno i to i to.

1498
00:49:02,579 --> 00:49:03,739
[SPEAKER_04] Nadnaravnu službu.

1499
00:49:03,739 --> 00:49:04,719
[SPEAKER_04] Oslobađaš zloduhe,

1500
00:49:04,719 --> 00:49:05,559
