1501
00:49:08,860 --> 00:49:13,179
[SPEAKER_04] U prvoj Korinčanima 4.20

1502
00:49:13,179 --> 00:49:14,199
[SPEAKER_04] kaže riječ Božja.

1503
00:49:14,199 --> 00:49:15,440
[SPEAKER_04] Ta nije u riječi

1504
