[SPEAKER_04] kraljevstvo Božje,

1505
00:49:16,579 --> 00:49:18,420
[SPEAKER_04] nego ovdje stoji

1506
00:49:18,420 --> 00:49:19,599
[SPEAKER_04] prijevod kreposti.

1507
00:49:19,599 --> 00:49:22,980
[SPEAKER_04] Jeronim nas je malo zafrkao

1508
00:49:22,980 --> 00:49:24,360
[SPEAKER_04] kad je preveo sa Virću.

1509
00:49:24,360 --> 00:49:26,920
[SPEAKER_04] To nije krepost,

1510
00:49:26,920 --> 00:49:27,960
[SPEAKER_04] nego je izvornik

1511
00:49:27,960 --> 00:49:29,000
[SPEAKER_04] koji je riječ dinamis,

1512
00:49:29,000 --> 00:49:31,960
[SPEAKER_04] gdje kaže snaga i moć.

1513
00:49:31,960 --> 00:49:34,760
[SPEAKER_04] Silna dijela.

1514
00:49:34,760 --> 00:49:36,659
[SPEAKER_04] Sila koja je potrebna

1515
00:49:36,659 --> 00:49:37,940
[SPEAKER_04] za čudesa i ozdravljenja.

1516
00:49:38,300 --> 00:49:40,099
[SPEAKER_04] Znači nije u riječi,

1517
00:49:40,099 --> 00:49:40,900
[SPEAKER_04] u navještaju,

1518
00:49:40,900 --> 00:49:41,420
[SPEAKER_04] u priči,

1519
00:49:41,420 --> 00:49:42,420
