1520
00:49:42,420 --> 00:49:43,920
[SPEAKER_04] koje možemo slušati

1521
00:49:43,920 --> 00:49:45,239
[SPEAKER_04] jedne i druge poučati,

1522
00:49:45,239 --> 00:49:46,980
[SPEAKER_04] nego u dinamisu,

1523
00:49:46,980 --> 00:49:47,420
[SPEAKER_04] u sili.

1524
00:49:47,420 --> 00:49:50,699
[SPEAKER_04] Klasičan primjer

1525
